The Ospreys traded Kevin Attaway and a 2025 1st round pick (ORL) to the Penguins for Brock Walker.
The Ospreys traded Brock Walker to the Badgers for Thatch Bruin.
The Ospreys traded Chris Elgin-Taylor, Alex Crenshaw, and a 2023 2nd round pick (ORL) to the Savages for Bobby Knight.
The Ospreys traded Thatch Bruin and a 2023 1st round pick (ORL) to the Shockers for Devon Walsh.
